      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was looking at some old photos today. i don't even recognize that person anymore. not just the face, but the spirit. it's like that version of me actually died a long time ago and i've just been a walking corpse ever since. just going through the motions of a life that doesn't even belong to me anymore.",
